data.description: Take a look at this gorgeous two story home located in the Ventanas of East El Paso. This over 2200 square ft home has 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. Enjoy a spacious and open living, dining and kitchen, perfect for gatherings and entertaining. All 4 sleeping quarters are on the second story, creating a private and cozy arrangement for you, family or guests. There are endless possibilities in the large backyard and the neighborhood boasts a huge family park just one minute away! This well kept home also comes with solar panels!! You will not want to miss out on this well priced, energy efficient, spacious home. Home sold AS-IS.
